msg: Bug Fix: The pagination controls at the top of the form are not rendered for "multi" forms but only for "list" forms.

author: veithen
msg: Attempt to fix the random build failure seen on Hudson. It appears that it sometimes happens that a test sends a message before the JMS transport is listening on the destination. This works fine for queues, but not for topics. Slightly modified the JMS transport to track the number of JMS message consumers and to wait for at least one to be ready.
